{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Here is the exact prompt you can copy and paste into your Shopify AI assistant.
    
    To ensure you have full control, I have explicitly instructed the AI to build this as a Custom Liquid Form with clear, labeled sections in the code. This will allow you to easily go in and add new questions, change text, or add more checkboxes without breaking the design.
    
    Copy and Paste This Prompt into Shopify AI:
    
    Please create a custom "Contact Form" section using Custom Liquid. The layout must perfectly match a high-end, luxury editorial aesthetic with a pure white background and massive, generous padding around the entire section.
    
    Make sure the code is highly modular and includes clear comments (e.g., <!-- ADD NEW TEXT FIELDS HERE --> and <!-- ADD NEW CHECKBOXES HERE -->) so I can easily modify the code, add new questions, and add new checkbox options later.
    
    Section Header Area (Center Aligned):
    
    Main Heading: "Co-Author Your Legacy" (Format in an elegant, thin Serif font like Cormorant Garamond, dark grey/black).
    
    Subheading: "Due to their exclusive nature, bespoke commissions are strictly limited." (Format in a thin Sans-serif font like Montserrat, very light grey).
    
    Form Styling Rules:
    
    All input labels must be thin Sans-serif, light grey, ALL CAPS, with extremely wide letter spacing (tracking).
    
    The text input fields must NOT have full box borders. They should only have a single, thin, light grey bottom border (underline style) with a transparent background.
    
    Add generous vertical spacing between each form row.
    
    Form Layout & Fields:
    
    Row 1 (2-Column Grid):
    
    Left Field Label: "FIRST & LAST NAME" (Type: text)
    
    Right Field Label: "PARTNER'S NAME" (Type: text)
    
    Row 2 (2-Column Grid):
    
    Left Field Label: "CORPORATE EMAIL" (Type: email)
    
    Right Field Label: "PHONE NUMBER" (Type: tel)
    
    Row 3 (1-Column, Full Width):
    
    Label: "WHAT MILESTONE EVENTS ARE WE STYLING YOU FOR?"
    
    Include 3 vertical checkboxes below this label. The checkbox text must be thin Sans-serif, light grey, ALL CAPS, with wide letter spacing.
    
    Checkbox 1: "THE ALTAR (BRIDAL COMMISSIONS)"
    
    Checkbox 2: "THE BOARDROOM (EXECUTIVE PRESENCE)"
    
    Checkbox 3: "GLOBAL ENGAGEMENTS & GALAS"
    
    Submit Button:
    
    Make the button full-width across the form.
    
    Style: Transparent background with a thin, light grey outline border.
    
    Button Text: "REQUEST COMMISSION" (Thin Sans-serif, ALL CAPS, wide letter spacing, dark text).
    
    Footer Text (Below Button):
    
    "All submissions are reviewed directly by The Atelier Concierge." (Format in a thin font, italics, light grey, center aligned).
    
    Please generate the complete HTML/CSS/Liquid code for this custom form section so I can paste it into my theme and easily add more questions to it.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    max-width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__inner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.form_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, serif;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.heading_font.weight }};
    font-style: {{ block.settings.heading_font.style }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.heading_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.heading_margin }}px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.body_font.weight }};
    font-style: {{ block.settings.body_font.style }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subheading_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.form_top_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.field_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.row_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }}--full {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.label_font_weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.label_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.label_color }};
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.label_letter_spacing }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.label_margin }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.input_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.input_color }};
    background-color: transparent;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: {{ block.settings.input_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.input_border_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.input_padding }}px 0;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    border-bottom-color: {{ block.settings.input_focus_color }};
  }

  .ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}::placeholder {
    color: {{ block.settings.placeholder_color }};
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__checkbox-group-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: {{ block.settings.checkbox_spacing }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.checkbox_group_margin }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__checkbox-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.checkbox_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.checkbox_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.checkbox_size }}px;
    border: {{ block.settings.checkbox_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.checkbox_border_color }};
    background-color: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}:checked {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.checkbox_checked_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.checkbox_checked_color }};
  }

  .ai-commission-form__checkbox-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.checkbox_label_weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.checkbox_label_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.checkbox_label_color }};
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.checkbox_letter_spacing }}px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__submit-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_font_weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.button_letter_spacing }}px;
    background-color: transparent;
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding }}px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.button_top_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__submit-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_border }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text }};
  }

  .ai-commission-form__footer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.footer_top_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__footer-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.body_font.weight }};
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.footer_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.footer_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__success-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    color: {{ block.settings.success_color }};
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.input_size }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.row_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-commission-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.error_color }};
    font-family: {{ block.settings.body_font.family }}, sans-serif;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.label_size }}px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.row_spacing }}px;
    }

    .ai-commission-form__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-commission-form__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheading_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}
  class="ai-commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  <div class="ai-commission-form__inner-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-commission-form__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <h2 class="ai-commission-form__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.heading }}
      </h2>
      <p class="ai-commission-form__subheading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {{ block.settings.subheading }}
      </p>
    </div>

    {%- form 'contact' -%}
      <input
        type="hidden"
        name="contact[form_type]"
        value="commission_request"
      >

      <div class="ai-commission-form__form-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <div class="ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-commission-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-commission-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.name_label }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="ai-commission-name-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[name]"
              class="ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              required
            >
          </div>

          <div class="ai-commission-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-commission-partner-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.partner_label }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="ai-commission-partner-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[partner_name]"
              class="ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-commission-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-commission-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.email_label }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="ai-commission-email-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[email]"
              class="ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              autocomplete="email"
              required
              {% if form.errors %}
                aria-invalid="true"
                aria-describedby="ai-commission-form-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              {% endif %}
            >
          </div>

          <div class="ai-commission-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label
              for="ai-commission-phone-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              class="ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
              {{ block.settings.phone_label }}
            </label>
            <input
              type="tel"
              id="ai-commission-phone-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              name="contact[phone]"
              class="ai-commission-form__input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              autocomplete="tel"
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-commission-form__row-{{ ai_gen_id }}--full">
          <div class="ai-commission-form__field-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <label class="ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.milestone_label }}
            </label>

            <div class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-group-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
                  id="ai-commission-bridal-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[milestone_bridal]"
                  value="The Altar (Bridal Commissions)"
                  class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-commission-bridal-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.checkbox_1_label }}
                </label>
              </div>

              <div class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
                  id="ai-commission-boardroom-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[milestone_boardroom]"
                  value="The Boardroom (Executive Presence)"
                  class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-commission-boardroom-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.checkbox_2_label }}
                </label>
              </div>

              <div class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
                  id="ai-commission-galas-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  name="contact[milestone_galas]"
                  value="Global Engagements & Galas"
                  class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                <label
                  for="ai-commission-galas-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  class="ai-commission-form__checkbox-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                >
                  {{ block.settings.checkbox_3_label }}
                </label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {%- if form.errors -%}
          <div
            id="ai-commission-form-error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            class="ai-commission-form__error-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
          >
            {{ form.errors.messages.email }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if form.posted_successfully? -%}
          <div class="ai-commission-form__success-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.success_message }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="ai-commission-form__submit-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
        >
          {{ block.settings.button_label }}
        </button>

        <div class="ai-commission-form__footer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <p class="ai-commission-form__footer-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {{ block.settings.footer_text }}
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- endform -%}
  </div>
</commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class CommissionForm{{ai_gen_id}} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.form = this.querySelector('form');
        if (this.form) {
          this.form.addEventListener('submit', this.handleSubmit.bind(this));
        }
      }

      handleSubmit(event) {
        const checkboxes = this.querySelectorAll('input[type="checkbox"]:checked');
        if (checkboxes.length === 0) {
          const milestoneLabel = this.querySelector('.ai-commission-form__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          if (milestoneLabel) {
            milestoneLabel.style.color = '{{ block.settings.error_color }}';
            setTimeout(() => {
              milestoneLabel.style.color = '{{ block.settings.label_color }}';
            }, 3000);
          }
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('commission-form-{{ ai_gen_id }}', CommissionForm{{ai_gen_id}});
  })();
</script>

